meanings: (알지 못하다) do not know, (이해하지 못하다) do not understand
(경험이 없다) have no experience, be ignorant of
It would not matter if I didn't know, if my guess is right
(관용)if my guess is right,in all probability,in all (human) likelihood,(십중팔구)in nine cases out of ten,ten to one,most likely[probably],nine-tenths (미·속)

meanings.meaning: I may lose land...but I never lose a minute.
